{"tid":47321,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[黑店詐騙更新][無法無天]igshop黑店詐騙行為2","createTime":"2016-12-20T09:16:48.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-21T19:11:38.000Z","uid":67588,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2a8fe354abdde6b50c8c201768de2a071dcb947c","tid":47321,"uid":67588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:16:48.000Z","msg":"事發既第三日<br />\n<br />\n第三位受害人既資料已經整理好<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">此post目的在於希望比到其他受害人知道 請廣傳 如有其他人得知自己出事冇錢又冇貨 請馬上dm ig account: antikeepersneaker<br />\n<br />\n各受害人已經報警 希望各位可以好心推一推<br />\n呢一單並非單一事件<br />\n店主有預謀咁食左受害人既錢<br />\n無法無天</span><br />\n<br />\n受害人買左4件貨<br />\n價值超過4000蚊既貨<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2C9b07p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2C9b07p.jpg&h=108a547b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而店主又以同一手段詢問受害人<br />\n是否退款<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CH74NXe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCH74NXe.jpg&h=a618b983&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但受害人認為加既錢唔多<br />\n仍然要貨<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/20/170410_071dd5ab08e50ab8d6578a6d7c86e2ff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F20%2F170410_071dd5ab08e50ab8d6578a6d7c86e2ff.jpg&h=dc3d06b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n受害人如常入數到店主既公司戶口<br />\n恆生戶口<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sz5z5zj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSz5z5zj.jpg&h=b404b71b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當受害人見到antikeepersneaker既ig出現時<br />\n馬上聯絡店主<br />\n但截至今日 仍然係冇人覆<br />\n<br />\n係今朝 20/12/2016 10點左右<br />\n店主已經將其whatsapp帳戶删除<br />\n所有msg都只有單tick<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">另外目前受害人數:<br />\n4人<br />\n<br />\n估計涉及金額超過10000元</span><br />\n<br />\n如果仼何人發現自己受騙出左事<br />\n請馬上direct message到ig account<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">IG: antikeepersneaker</span><br />\n<br />\n店舖資料ig shop: Keepersneaker (已改名) <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jz9x15v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJz9x15v.jpg&h=0252c8bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現時為: Hongkongtgt<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/20/170605_fd3d6acce35080a77f4e6b841dbb39b3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F20%2F170605_fd3d6acce35080a77f4e6b841dbb39b3.jpg&h=806cae40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後再改名為 igshop: love_life429<br />\n<br />\n最新資料(19/12/2016 11:45) :該igshop已將其帳戶删除<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/028G007.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F028G007.jpg&h=bdd1fc10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n該店係19/12/2016 晚上10時幾貼出最後一個po 但唔夠一小時後帳戶即被删除<br />\n<br />\n犯罪手法:<br />\n主要以因為計算價錢出錯為理由，向受害人表示要加錢，聲稱會退款但最終無疾而終<br />\n受害人無法聯絡店主 而受害人嘗試在貼文留言亦被删除以及封鎖帳戶<br />\n另外 即使受害人仍然要件貨 但去到依家已經無疾而終 錢貨兩樣都冇哂<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">電話 (只有whatsapp) : 9558 5373</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/20/170658_f8111882a7d4035b6cd1239e2d960826.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F20%2F170658_f8111882a7d4035b6cd1239e2d960826.jpg&h=5c0548b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n銀行戶口<br />\n滙豐銀行 124 411 836 838<br />\n恆生銀行 789 287 638 883<br />\n<br />\n受害人2號<br />\n<br />\n向店主訂購貨品<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/20/170714_ea3abfd41a54cbdc9921e7f3831d3483.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F20%2F170714_ea3abfd41a54cbdc9921e7f3831d3483.jpg&h=c7607078&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pw8Fvh0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPw8Fvh0.jpg&h=00cb13d1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/560R3py.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F560R3py.jpg&h=29d48e47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n受害人揀岩貨品之後<br />\n店主有意引誘受害人買多幾件貨<br />\n佢可以食到既錢就越大<br />\n透過銀行入數 匯款大約1900比店主<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/20/170732_ea7e957363e54451409255edb4c1488c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F20%2F170732_ea7e957363e54451409255edb4c1488c.jpg&h=648e21ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但當受害人再詢問貨品幾時有之際<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A8BDjgc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA8BDjgc.jpg&h=ce180093&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n店主已經第6日冇回覆受害人<br />\n<br />\nPost 1"},{"pid":"7da88d1e6539bd10303c8aa03e755e10fe627cd1","tid":47321,"uid":67588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:17:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihk-forum.firebaseapp.com/thread/46513/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flihk-forum.firebaseapp.com%2Fthread%2F46513%2Fpage%2F1&d=xUcJZgEr%2B061WxnRHYnldJkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=5be6729e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihk-forum.firebaseapp.com/thread/46513/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"c169ec657a6ab097ec59d095d0a38ecd3a4eae69","tid":47321,"uid":67588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:18:06.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"71afcef5729b6e86d6a056dd134cdcf894135b04","tid":47321,"uid":13474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:34:40.000Z","msg":"報左警未？"},{"pid":"cab41b519ff0cc1674e0ce4a1f26b38aa591eea7","tid":47321,"uid":65233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:41:21.000Z","msg":"幫手推一推<br />\n自己都有搞ig shop<br />\n呢d 垃圾真係害人不淺"},{"pid":"4d6379d84afc2b65b7a29558b2bf7e5205518cc6","tid":47321,"uid":67588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:41:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>報左警未？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n已報"},{"pid":"d77ad7c7c01e47fc0268c8721bd2e376393bb8d0","tid":47321,"uid":67588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite